<h2 class="project__step-title">Broadcast and Arena Design</h2>
<div class="side-by-side">
  <p>
    While on-site at the arena, I built a dynamic motion design system for the
    event's video features, broadcast loops, stingers, and arena billboards.
    With access to developer builds, I captured in-game environments, composited
    seamless loops, and in collaboration with designer Mateo Julia-Wise, we
    rendered extra-wide motion graphics for the massive triple screens at
    Esports Arena, and the various digital billboards throughout the stadium.
  </p>
  <p>
    With the event video and design locked and shipped off to the control room,
    all that was left for me to do was attend the event as a videographer,
    capturing on-the-fly interviews and a wealth of footage for the dev team to
    use on further promotion of the title.
  </p>
</div>
